OL,3,CSon uncovers his father's wartime
OL,4,Cjourney in WW1
OL,6,FWe now know Arthur fought in the ill-
OL,7,Ffated Gallipoli campaign in Western
OL,8,FTurkey in 1916.
OL,10,FFought during the First World War,
OL,11,FGallipoli was the first major
OL,12,Famphibious operation in modern warfare.
OL,14,FBritish Empire and French troops
OL,15,Flanded on the Ottoman-held peninsula
OL,16,Fin the Dardanelles Straits with
OL,17,Fdisastrous consequences for the Allies.
