OL,3,CSon uncovers his father's wartime
OL,4,Cjourney in WW1
OL,6,FSteve said: "This is what we do. This
OL,7,Fis how we try to tell these stories
OL,8,Ffor people like Roy who's now in his
OL,9,F90's.
OL,11,F"He now understands what his father
OL,12,Fwent through and knows where his
OL,13,Ffather was and that to me is a really
OL,14,Fbig part of what the Roll is all
OL,15,Fabout."
OL,17,FLt Arthur Bradley died aged 56, in
OL,18,F1958.
